PortSystem 1.0
name			hfstar
version			1.13.19
categories		sysutils
maintainers		waqar@opendarwin.org
description		gnutar with HFS+ support
homepage		http://www.metaobject.com/Community.html
platforms		darwin
long_description	A version of gnutar for Mac OS X that supports \
                        archiving HFS+ specific information such as resource \
                        forks, type and creator codes as well as other finder \
                        flags.

